{"lemma":"إِرثُ","slug":"إِرثُ","root":"#.ر.ث","root_slug":"_-ر-ث","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ر-ث","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n538","n539","n541","n41835","n14736","n14741"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A5%D9%90%D8%B1%D8%AB%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n538","headword_ar":"اَرَثَ","root":"Arv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 2."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n539","headword_ar":"ارّث","root":"Arv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^oriyvN","text_ar":"تَاْرِيثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He kindled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lighted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a fire; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to burn, burn up, burn brightly"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fiercely, blaze,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flame;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arava","text_ar":"اَرَثَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arovN","text_ar":"اَرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K; in a copy of the A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovN","text_ar":"اـِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) but this [says SM] no leading lexicographer has mentioned, nor have I found any example of it. (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"war~ava","text_ar":"وَرَّثَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tA^ryv","text_ar":"تاريث"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exciting discord, dissension, disorder, strife, quarrelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"animosity, between a people."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^rav bayona","text_ar":"ارَث بَيْنَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alqawomi","text_ar":"القَوْمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, A,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^r~v bayonahumu Al$~ar~a waAlHaroba","text_ar":"ارّث بَيْنَهُمُ الشَّرَّ وَالحَرْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He excited discord, dissension, disorder, strife, quarrelling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"animosity, between,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among, the people,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"company of men;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M, A;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kindled the fire of discord, dissension,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"evil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"war,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"between them,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, * TA.)"}],"source_refs":["M","A","T","S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n541","headword_ar":"اـِرْثٌ","root":"Arv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inheritance;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or a person's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obtaining possession of property left to"},{"kind":"text","text":"him"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by one who has died."},{"kind":"text","text":"(MF.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An inheritance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a heritage; what is inherited."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An old condition, case,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state of things, which the last has inherited from the first."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K.) So in the phrase,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa EalaY A_irovK mino ka*aA","text_ar":"هُوَ عَلَى اـِرْثٍ مِنْ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is conforming, in respect of such a thing, with an old state of things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an old usage, which he has inherited from his ancestors"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) And in the following ex., from a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~akumo EalaY A_irovK mino","text_ar":"اـِنَّكُمْ عَلَى اـِرْثٍ مِنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovi A^abiykumo A_iboraAhiyma","text_ar":"اـِرْثِ اَبِيكُمْ اـِبْرَاهِيمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily ye are conforming with an old state of things,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an old usage, which ye have inherited from your father Abraham"},{"kind":"text","text":"], the meaning is, that his religion was their heritage. (T, * TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A remainder,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what remains,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, L, K,) of a thing, (K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the original"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing: (M, L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iraAvN","text_ar":"اـِرَاثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (L.) ―         -b5-  And [hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ashes."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b6-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Origin, race,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, A, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa fiY A_irovi SidoqK","text_ar":"هُوَ فِى اـِرْثِ صِدْقٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is of an excellent origin, race,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stock."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu lafiY A_irovi majodK","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَفِى اـِرْثِ مَجْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is of a glorious origin, race,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stock"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irofi majodK","text_ar":"اـِرْفِ مَجْدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", by a change of letters. (Yaa- koob, M.) Accord. to IAar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_irovN","text_ar":"اـِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"relates to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasab","text_ar":"حَسَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or grounds of pretension to respect or honour, on account of one's ancestors' or one's own deeds or qualities, &c.]; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", to property, or wealth. (M.) [See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wrv","text_ar":"ورث"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","L","K"]},{"entry_id":"n41835","headword_ar":"اـِرْثٌ","root":"wrv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wirovN","text_ar":"وِرْثٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and 1."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n14736","headword_ar":"ارثّ","root":"rv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see above, in two places. ―         -b2-  Also, said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His rope was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, old, and worn out."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Arv~hu","text_ar":"ارثّهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. wear, attrition, or wear and tear, (Th, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rendered it old, and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bad;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Th, M;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"threadbare, shabby,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mean;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) namely, anything, but mostly used in relation to what is worn as clothing, or spread as furniture. (M.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Th","M"]},{"entry_id":"n14741","headword_ar":"اَرَثُّ","root":"rv","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rav~N","text_ar":"رَثٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}